<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='513957' id='t-513957'>such as fear, guilt, shame</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='517836' id='t-517836'>and maybe a little bit of liar's delight.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:51
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='520956' id='t-520956'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='523682' id='t-523682'>Unfortunately, such emotions
are either fleeting or hidden.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='528546' id='t-528546'>Therefore, it's mostly invisible to us.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:02
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='531669' id='t-531669'>So in the last five years,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='533052' id='t-533052'>we have been trying to figure out a way
