<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='536972' id='t-536972'>Then we made a discovery.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:10
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='539273' id='t-539273'>We know that underneath our facial skin,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='542482' id='t-542482'>there's a rich network of blood vessels.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='545900' id='t-545900'>When we experience different emotions,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='548341' id='t-548341'>our facial blood flow changes subtly.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='551613' id='t-551613'>And these changes are regulated
by the autonomic system</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='555585' id='t-555585'>that is beyond our conscious control.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='558159' id='t-558159'>By looking at facial blood flow changes,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='562006' id='t-562006'>we can reveal people's hidden emotions.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='565229' id='t-565229'>Unfortunately, such emotion-related
facial blood flow changes</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='570031' id='t-570031'>are too subtle to detect by our naked eye.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='573632' id='t-573632'>So to help us reveal
people's facial emotions,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='577424' id='t-577424'>we have developed a new imaging technology</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='580482' id='t-580482'>we call &quot;transdermal optical imaging.&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:55
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='584679' id='t-584679'>To do so, we use a regular
