<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='646415' id='t-646415'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:58
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='647446' id='t-647446'>This is the real Pinocchio effect.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='649592' id='t-649592'>When people lie,</span>
