</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:10
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='659379' id='t-659379'>Of course, lying is not the only situation</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='662910' id='t-662910'>that will evoke our hidden emotions.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='665782' id='t-665782'>So then we asked ourselves,</span>
