<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='670051' id='t-670051'>how can our technology be used?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='673027' id='t-673027'>One application is in education.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='676597' id='t-676597'>For example, using this technology,
