<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='728977' id='t-728977'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:21
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='730541' id='t-730541'>For example, during a debate.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='733220' id='t-733220'>Well, the answer is yes.</span>
